            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Haec cava saxa Oppilani <lb n="2"/>continet menbra <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/>claro nitore natalium <lb n="4"/>gestu <expan><abbr>abituq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> co<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>s<supplied reason="lost">picu</supplied>um <lb n="5"/>opib<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> quippe pollens et ar<lb break="no" n="6"/>tuum virib<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> cluens <lb n="7"/>iacula vehi precipitur <expan><abbr>predoq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>Bacceis destinatur <lb n="9"/>in procinctum <note>sic</note> belli necatur <lb n="10"/>opitulatione sodalium desolatus <lb n="11"/>naviter cede perculsum <lb n="12"/>clintes <note>sic</note> rapiunt peremtum <lb n="13"/>exanimis domu reducitur <lb n="14"/>suis a vernulis humatur <lb n="15"/>lugit <note>sic</note> coniux cum liberis <lb n="16"/>fletib<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> familia prestrepit <note>sic</note> <lb n="17"/>decies ut ternos ad quater <lb n="18"/>quaternos vixit per annos <lb n="19"/>pridie Septembium <note>sic</note> Idus <lb n="20"/>morte a Vasconibus multat<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="21"/>era sescentensima et octagensima <lb n="22"/>id gestum memento <lb n="23"/>sepultus sub <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ie</ex></expan> quiescit <lb n="24"/>VI <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Octubres <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Todestag am 12. September 642 n. Chr.; Tag. der Beisetzung wie oben angegeben.</p>
            </div>
